text:
The seats are quite empty...
Should we sit?

You can sleep until we arrive. The shoot earlier
started early, so you must have woken up quite early, right?

...I see.
But I'm glad today's shoot went smoothly.

It seems like a popular magazine,
so I think a lot of people will notice it.
I wonder if Noctchill's name will get out there too...!

Ah, definitely.
We'll have to work harder so more people can learn about it.
